82fbad5a395879ba4dac4aa015271522a832da126f7ec204274821d78100ed17c4047bf4d1526f82e7785bdf9d375741eecfe4cd24f3c5dcdcabc2c7cd01f67d  cryptography_vectors-47.0.0.tar.gz
be7b102bf2220913996ee934a506c2f989c47e1e7f7c05b17848cd75ffbe6e396d1f46510bde37c2079f7a576c1f157190aef5f5fa17431bf231dcd08a52efaa  vectors-build-backend-flit_core_patch
"
